Vertemax is HAKI's innovative and market-leading edge protection system offering a range of solutions designed to protect your workforce with the best collective protection solutions and fall arrest safety to help prevent accidents associated with working at height.  

While each product meets EN, COHS, OSHA, and ANSI-ASSE standards, our product ranges are designed for great versatility, high productivity, easy assembly, ease of storage and transportation (to and around sites) and can be customised to your needs.
Use the interactive points to explore our products. Click on blue markers for more information.

ELEBIA LIFTING 1

Elebia 1

A market leader in automatic crane hooks. The Elebia range allows operators to manoeuvre their hook remotely, removing the need for manual handling and eliminating the associated dangers.
